quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  23,33,"Sano achinkulungwa mu ŵandu ŵakwe aŵala ŵaŵakufuulu ni kanila yakusimangana ni Akhera soni ni twasichilisye pa umi waduniya, ŵatite: “Nganijuŵa aju ikaŵeje mundu mpela jenumanja, jukulyaga mu ichindu yankuilyaga jenumanja, soni jukumwaga mu ichindu yankumwaga.”"
  23,34,"“Soni chisimu naga nkwika mwakun’jitika mundu mpela jenumanja, chisimu ŵanganyammwe pa jele ndemajo tim’be ŵakwasika.”"
  23,35,"“Ana akumpa chilanga chanti chisimu ŵanganyammwe patinchiwapo ni kusyuka litaka ni maupa, kuti chisimu jenumanja chinchikoposyedwa m’malembe?”"
  23,36,"“Ili kwanaula, ili kwanaula yankupedwa chilangayo (nganiiŵa itendekwe ata panandi).”"
  23,37,"“Pangali (umi) wine ikaŵeje umi wetu waduniyapeuno, tukuwaga, nambo soni tukulamaga, soni nganituŵa uwwe ŵanti ni kuukulidwa m’malembe.”"
  23,38,"“Nganijuŵa aju (jwaakuliŵilanjila utumeju) ikaŵeje mundu jwansepele Allah unami, soni uwwe nganituŵa tunkulupilile jwalakwe.”"
  23,39,"(Hudu) jwatite: “Ambuje ŵangu! Munjenjelani ligongo lyakunganila.”"
  23,40,"(Allah) jwatite: “Pangakaŵapa taŵe ŵakuligamba.”"
  23,41,"Basi ni wakwembekenye n’gumilo (waipotesi) mwakuonaonape, basi ni twatesile kuŵa mpela iswani (yakujigalwa ni mesi), basi chonasiko chakunaula chaliji kwa ŵandu ŵalupuso"
  23,42,Kaneko twagumbile panyuma pao mikutula jine
  23,43,Pangali umati wampaka ujijanguye kapena kujichelewasya ndema jakwe (jakuwila)
  23,44,"Kaneko twatumisye achimitenga Ŵetu mwakuyana. Ndema ni katema kajwauŵichililaga umati uliose ntenga jwakwe ŵankanilaga, ni twaakuyichisyaga ŵane panyuma pa ŵane (wa kuchonasiko), ni twatesile ŵanganyao kuŵa ngani (sisyesyene syaŵandu ŵakala syakwajamuka nasyo ŵandu ŵasambano), basi chonasiko chakunaula chaliji kwa ŵandu ŵangakulupilila"
  23,45,"Kaneko twantumisye Musa ni nkulugwe Haruna, pamo ni isimosimo Yetu kwisa soni umboni wakuonechela"
  23,46,"Kwa Firiauna ni nduna syakwe, nambo ŵanganyao ŵalikwesyisye ni ŵaliji soni ŵandu ŵakulinyakula"
  23,47,"Basi ŵanganyao ŵatite: “Ana twakulupilile ŵandu ŵaŵili ŵanti mpela uwwewe, kutendaga ŵandu ŵao kukwetu ali achikapolo!”"
  23,48,"Mwanti ŵaakaaniile ŵanaŵaŵilio, basi ni ŵaliji (akukanilao) mwa akonanjidwa"
  23,49,Soni chisimu Uwwe twampele Musa Chitabu kuti ŵanganyao ajongoche
  23,50,"Soni twantesile Mwanache jwa Maryam kwisa soni Mamagwe kuŵa chisimosimo (chakulosya ukombosi Wetu, wakomboleka ŵakongwe kuŵeleka mwanache mwangali kusimana ni ŵalume), ni twajuyiye ŵanaŵaŵilio pachikwesya chakutamilichika ni ntunjelele, chachakwete soni achitutumule (pa Baitul Muqaddas)"